 black">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>\n<h2 style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:black;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Associated_Wikimedia"><i>Associated Wikimedia</i></span></h2>\n</div>\n<div style="border: 1px solid #df0000; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">\n<div class="noprint" style="text-align:center;">\n<div style="display:inline-block;margin:0 0 0.75em 0">\n<p style="margin:0">The following <a href="/wiki/Wikimedia_Foundation" title="Wikimedia Foundation">Wikimedia Foundation</a> sister projects provide more on this subject:</p>\n<div style="float:left; margin:0 3px 3px 3px; font-size:91%;">\n<p><b><a href="https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Special:Search/Weapons_of_mass_destruction" class="extiw" title="wikibooks:Special:Search/Weapons of mass destruction">Wikibooks</a></b><br />\nBooks<br /></p>\n<div class="center">\n<div class="floatnone"><a href="https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Special:Search/Weapons_of_mass_destruction"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/25px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png" width="25" height="25" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/38px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikibooks-logo.svg/50px-Wikibooks-logo.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="300" data-file-height="300" /></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style="float:left; margin:0 3px 3px 3px; font-size:91%;">\n<p><b><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/Category:Weapons_of_mass_destruction" class="extiw" title="commons:Special:Search/Category:Weapons of mass destruction">Commons</a></b><br />\nMedia<br /></p>\n<div class="center">\n<div class="floatnone"><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/Category:Weap